description:
1, Sempai`s Discomfort: Sempai`s mortal enemy? Her big sister appears!
2, Pop Quiz Sempai: Sempai wears a flower print.
3, Conquering Sempai: Senpai really gives birth this time.
4, Kimono Sempai: Lots of wazuma.
5, Sempai Off Campus: An outdoor survival game?
